All of sudden Seekker jumps down from above.  "I can fly i can fly" 
he said as he plummeted face first into the dirt.  Standing up and 
dusting himself off, he spoke to himself outloud.  "I guess not"  
He then saw the new bots, then turning to Lokk and Axis said 
"What the blazes are you doing jsut standing there.  ATTACK!" he 
yelled as he jumped aroud Axis and pushed him at the stranger.
